                     <interp inst="t18201206-44-person464" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I lodged over the prisoner. About six o'clock I came home, saw the door open, and the furniture gone.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18201206-44-person465">
                  JOHN 
                  BARNS
               <interp inst="t18201206-44-person465" type="surname" value="BARNS"></interp>
